在分子生物学中，'''Lon蛋白酶家族'''是一个依赖ATP的[[丝氨酸蛋白酶|丝氨酸蛋白酶]][[蛋白质家族|家族]]，在[[细菌|细菌]]、[[古菌|古菌]]以及[[真核生物|真核生物]]中都有发现。在[[真核生物|真核生物]]中，大部分的Lon蛋白酶都定位于[[线粒体基质|线粒体基质]]<ref name="pmid8248235">{{cite journal | author = Wang N, Gottesman S, Willingham MC, Gottesman MM, Maurizi MR | title = A human mitochondrial ATP-dependent protease that is highly homologous to bacterial Lon protease | journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. | volume = 90 | issue = 23 | pages = 11247–51 | pmid = 8248235 | pmc = 47959 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.90.23.11247| url = |date=December 1993}}</ref><ref name="pmid9620272">{{cite journal | author = Barakat S, Pearce DA, Sherman F, Rapp WD | title = Maize contains a Lon protease gene that can partially complement a yeast pim1-deletion mutant | journal = Plant Mol. Biol. | volume = 37 | issue = 1 | pages = 141–54 | pmid = 9620272 | doi = | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-molecular-biology_1998-05_37_1/page/141|date=May 1998}}</ref>。在[[釀酒酵母|釀酒酵母]]中，Lon蛋白酶PIM1定位于[[线粒体基质|线粒体基质]]，是[[线粒体|线粒体]]功能所必需的。PIM1通常为基础性[[基因表現|表达]]，但在热胁迫增加时表达量会增加，这表示PIM1可能和{{le|热休克|heat shock}}反应有关<ref name="pmid8276800">{{cite journal | author = Van Dyck L, Pearce DA, Sherman F | title = PIM1 encodes a mitochondrial ATP-dependent protease that is required for mitochondrial function in the yeast Saccharomyces cerevisiae | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 269 | issue = 1 | pages = 238–42 | pmid = 8276800 | doi = | url = |date=January 1994}}</ref>。

